item.dc:creator: @whackatre Whackatre
item.description:
@whackatre wrote:

[quote=“Assassins Creed Fan, post:4, topic:417191”]I actually love the Junkbot concept (Overall because it looks like the train ticket dispensers that we have here) but if I take a closer look at his legs and feet, I see that they overlap eachother, just 2 primitives that are slammed onto each other.
And for the recycling’ish logo on his side as far as I can see, it also overlaps his Body/Head.
If you improve those points, I would love it even more.[/quote]

Thanks, how do I improve the overlapped shapes?

item.dc:creator: @Assassins_Creed_Fan Assassins Creed Fan
item.description:
@Assassins_Creed_Fan wrote:

I actually love the Junkbot concept (Overall because it looks like the train ticket dispensers that we have here) but if I take a closer look at his legs and feet, I see that they overlap eachother, just 2 primitives that are slammed onto each other.
And for the recycling’ish logo on his side as far as I can see, it also overlaps his Body/Head.
If you improve those points, I would love it even more.
